N.Y. Comp. Codes R. & Regs. Tit. 2 ยง 18.15 - Approvable voucher

State Regulations

An approvable voucher is a voucher submitted by an agency
in such form and supported by such substantiating documentation as the

Comptroller may reasonably require. Notes
